<section xml:id="C4.S18">
<title>Inequalities</title>          
<paragraph xml:id="C4.S18.Px1">
<title>Jordan’s Inequality</title>    
<para xml:id="C4.S18.Px1.p1">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="1" xml:id="C4.S18.Px1.p1.s1">
 <Math equation-number="4.18.1" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S18.E1">\frac{2x}{\pi}\leq\sin x\leq x, if 0\leq x\leq\frac{1}{2}\pi</Math>.
</sentence>

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="2" sentence-num-in-section="2" xml:id="C4.S18.Px1.p1.s2">
<Math equation-number="4.18.2" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S18.E2">x\leq\tan x, if 0\leq x&lt;\frac{1}{2}\pi,</Math> <Math equation-number="4.18.3" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S18.E3">\cos x\leq\frac{\sin x}{x}\leq 1, if 0\leq x\leq\pi,</Math> <Math equation-number="4.18.4" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S18.E4">\pi&lt;\frac{\sin\left(\pi x\right)}{x(1-x)}\leq 4, if 0&lt;x&lt;1</Math>.
</sentence>

</para>

 
<para xml:id="C4.S18.Px1.p2">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="3" xml:id="C4.S18.Px1.p2.s1">
With <Math mode="inline" xml:id="C4.S18.Px1.p2.m1">z=x+iy</Math> , <Math equation-number="4.18.5" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S18.E5">|\sinh y|\leq|\sin z|\leq\cosh y,</Math> <Math equation-number="4.18.6" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S18.E6">|\sinh y|\leq|\cos z|\leq\cosh y,</Math> <Math equation-number="4.18.7" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S18.E7">|\csc z|\leq\operatorname{csch}|y|,</Math> <Math equation-number="4.18.8" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S18.E8">|\cos z|\leq\cosh|z|,</Math> <Math equation-number="4.18.9" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S18.E9">|\sin z|\leq\sinh|z|,</Math> <Math equation-number="4.18.10" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S18.E10">|\cos z|&lt;2,|\sin z|\leq\tfrac{6}{5}|z|, , if |z|&lt;1</Math>.
</sentence>

</para>
 
<para xml:id="C4.S18.Px1.p3">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="4" xml:id="C4.S18.Px1.p3.s1">
For more inequalities see Mitrinović (1964, pp. 101–111),Mitrinović (1970, pp. 235–265), andBullen (1998, pp. 250–254).
</sentence>

</para>
 
